                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City policeman,</hi> 33). I produce a certificate of Allen's conviction here (<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Nov.</hi>, 1849, <hi rend="italic">of stealing a handkerchief; confined nine months</hi>)—I was present—he is the person.</p>
